      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>City directories usually contain an alphabetical list of businesses and residents for a municipality. Names of heads of households are included and in some cases, death dates, partners in firms, or forwarding addresses. Often these also include advertisements, information about schools, churches, and social organizations.</Note_Text>
